  "prompt": "Which phone should I buy under INR 15K?",
  "response": "As of the latest updates, there are several good options for smartphones under INR 15,000 in India. Here are some popular choices you might consider:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo Series**: Realme's Narzo series often includes budget-friendly models with decent specifications. Look for the latest model available within your budget.\n\n2. **Xiaomi Redmi Note Series**: The Redmi Note series is known for offering good value for money. The Note 11 or similar models might be within this price range.\n\n3. **Poco M Series**: Poco, a Xiaomi sub-brand, offers devices with strong performance features at competitive prices.\n\n4. **Samsung Galaxy M Series**: Samsung's M series targets budget-conscious consumers and often offers good battery life and decent specs.\n\n5. **Moto G Series**: Motorola's G series is known for providing a clean Android experience and solid build quality.\n\n6. **Infinix and Tecno Models**: These brands have been increasing their presence in the budget segment with feature-rich phones.\n\nWhen considering a purchase, check for the latest model releases and compare specifications like battery life, camera quality, display, and processing power. Additionally, read user reviews and consider your specific needs to ensure you get the best phone for your requirements.",
